{"tid":1721933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實中大用區選做籌碼好合理 而家停課半停擺嘅狀態政府其實大條道理取消區選","createTime":"2019-11-14T19:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T04:21:52.000Z","uid":26179,"like":57,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"1a9e990134783121091b2fd550fe2a71dd1bc049","tid":1721933,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:48:51.000Z","msg":"五大訴求唔係兩條路仔就換到<br />\n反而咁樣係中大手足向政府示強<br />\n話畀佢哋知我哋有能力談判<br />\n同時保住區選<br />\n而且更加可以同全世界講我哋唔係唔講道理<br />\n只要政府願意回應<br />\n我哋就會讓步<br />\n咁樣反而仲可以搶到啲所謂中立嘅民意翻嚟<br />\n亦都直線反駁咗政府一直以來所為要先止暴制亂先回應到訴求嘅論調<br />\n<br />\n而家開得一條一定又會塞死<br />\n無阻和你塞三罷<br />\n成件事根本合理到爆<br />\n甚至可以話係高招<br />\n唔明其他post啲人屌啲咩<br />\n<br />\n建議埋大手足可以參考吓<br />\n開一條紅隧<br />\n免費畀人過<br />\n換咩可以再諗"},{"pid":"140290f4bc4c5d71b41b003f68349386636531cd","tid":1721933,"uid":26179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:50:04.000Z","msg":"推到埋大見到"},{"pid":"bade63469af36d391b7de7ff47acc7b46eb6a198","tid":1721933,"uid":26179,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:50:37.000Z","msg":"唔明連登仔屌乜"},{"pid":"d44b240f5d402406c3c3d9600ca2fcf864831e67","tid":1721933,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:53:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4654f9f54a0cc79c5f19a14b842a1b3a2e4b4c99","tid":1721933,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:55:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cca57b4ed5eb783eda2e2bf418ab27a77a392f66","tid":1721933,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:56:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10e3a39a9a14ed223706e3eba33ee851e675c604","tid":1721933,"uid":142249,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:57:14.000Z","msg":"全力支持中大手足決定<br />\n不分化 不割"},{"pid":"7379a10af5ee6588971eb0ef0dfe3bb6383c8237","tid":1721933,"uid":102185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.